    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six unassessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The literature review confirms that the CFD hemolysis model produces predictions consistent with published benchmarks for analogous centrifugal pump geometries. The relative hemolysis index QoI is directly relevant to the regulatory decision criterion. The assessment team concludes that the model has sufficient credibility for the CPB COU and recommends acceptance of the simulation results for the 510(k) submission.",
